{"tid":36714,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖, 九龍塘練習三手軚掉頭的問題","createTime":"2016-12-13T01:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T08:33:00.000Z","uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"427e23e331983dec14162bc9d2a20b833b764acb","tid":36714,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"如圖, 其實要用黃線(窄D) 定 白線 (灁D) 來當做邊位?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/rza3aut79/U_TURN_KLN_TONG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Frza3aut79%2FU_TURN_KLN_TONG.jpg&h=8ae05381&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c38d66e4f8c94bdd0d62313dc2d9281f43daf02","tid":36714,"uid":64602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如圖, 其實要用黃線(窄D) 定 白線 (灁D) 來當做邊位?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/rza3aut79/U_TURN_KLN_TONG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Frza3aut79%2FU_TURN_KLN_TONG.jpg&h=8ae05381&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係白線"},{"pid":"1e603adbe2497be6df07e9a913a7f670a20a389c","tid":36714,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"白線"},{"pid":"68885b9443c173285bada3e75ba7563f8ecf1a02","tid":36714,"uid":24632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:57:33.000Z","msg":"之前聽師傅講白線係貨van，黃線係私家車"},{"pid":"defaa30d6da6c0e66555bbbae3249e13681c6c06","tid":36714,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"其實最主要係識得控制速度，一味靠慢，車慢軚快，就算架車停喺條路中間都一樣可以三手軚掉到個頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1fdf2f723bccdd303f212058fc22987f9b70cd","tid":36714,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"白線"},{"pid":"9978b1abc22f466ff7dcfa60c8f8998eb9d168fa","tid":36714,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"去試場實地掉頭學啦"},{"pid":"85e7ee0f5cf0d4788905f2e6380d2335e6d017c3","tid":36714,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去試場實地掉頭學啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔到個學生話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1693d69f8d2e6951f07d28f1bfea168278c10d87","tid":36714,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去試場實地掉頭學啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔到個學生話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又真<br />\n但如果考天光道成日要排隊<br />\n最好去試場練，仲要係斜路掉頭"},{"pid":"e2b11c6e9e19b4b55ad3751ce0267c67862b6840","tid":36714,"uid":43563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"天光道個三手掉頭條斜路闊好多，你係到掉到，去到一定得<br />\n利申:前日1 take pass 咗"},{"pid":"f3286c1230cc36cebbb0722bac55be156db67afd","tid":36714,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去試場實地掉頭學啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔到個學生話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又真<br />\n但如果考天光道成日要排隊<br />\n最好去試場練，仲要係斜路掉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我考澤安，點入試場練?"},{"pid":"6b0d0f9ca0daceacb32cc957944fdc3225fe984e","tid":36714,"uid":4755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T22:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔到個學生話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又真<br />\n但如果考天光道成日要排隊<br />\n最好去試場練，仲要係斜路掉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我考澤安，點入試場練?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無得入去練，澤安出面有個位練，不過始終同試場差少少<br />\n我考個陣都係驚泊位掉頭多過驚路試，加油啦！<br />\n<br />\n利申：澤安1 take pass"},{"pid":"d3a234882119cc6bba361f11d6d77c6c38747b5b","tid":36714,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又真<br />\n但如果考天光道成日要排隊<br />\n最好去試場練，仲要係斜路掉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我考澤安，點入試場練?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無得入去練，澤安出面有個位練，不過始終同試場差少少<br />\n我考個陣都係驚泊位掉頭多過驚路試，加油啦！<br />\n<br />\n利申：澤安1 take pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3250e4bb3994778580155503cd930695ae4ecb","tid":36714,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:38:29.000Z","msg":"好驚斜路起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc912d3832f65b9c003993a7ff9afe6d206ed7e","tid":36714,"uid":20717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"第二手回多小小 第三手就好易出"},{"pid":"b7942d28e87660d222fc87073bcc12f6135a3e39","tid":36714,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好驚斜路起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n升高極力子直到feel到部車向前chok一chok<br />\n同一時間部車會微震，咁就停<br />\n望鏡同盲點，然後放手制<br />\n有機會放手制後部車唔陏，咁就慢慢放極力子同時慢慢比油<br />\n哩個方法易掌握又穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}